  "message": "feat(agentic-flow): Update to RuvLLM 0.2.4 and AgentDB 2.0.0-alpha.3.3\n\n- Update @ruvector/ruvllm to 0.2.4 (fixed stats, SIMD inference)\n- Update agentdb to 2.0.0-alpha.3.3 (RuvLLM LLMRouter integration)\n\nRuvLLM features now available via AgentDB LLMRouter:\n- Local CPU+SIMD inference (no API keys needed)\n- SONA adaptive learning\n- HNSW memory integration\n- FastGRNN routing\n- 384/768/1024-dim embeddings\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
